name: Modern digital Expressionism with Pop Art

metadata.name: 2TheMax
metadata.description:
An NFT created as an homage to the 2022 F1 championship won by Max Verstappen. I created a racing texture and used that to render out the whole scene. The subject is wearing a racing helmet and cheering number 1.

This high resolution artwork comes with a commercial license, so the collector can earn back the investment and more people get to see the art.  
Read the license here:  
https://foundation.app/@ArjenRoos/nftcl/1
